      "content": "look i'm not trying to be difficult but i've literally taken 800mg of ibuprofen before with no issues at all. people take like 1200mg or more for dental surgery or something all the time right? i just really need some relief so i can function tomorrow. is there a way to safely combine them just this once so i can actually get some sleep? just tell me what would be the most effective way to do it.",
